item.title: Changed were you start out on your sever
item.dc:creator: @madgamer madgamer
item.description:
@madgamer wrote:

go into player.java and search or scroll down till you see a code like this

// initial x and y coordinates of the player heightLevel = 0; // the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet teleportToX = 3253; teleportToY = 3424;

Then just change the numbers to the coordinates you want to be the starting point.
